even though you may feel it strange

23:23.824 --> 23:26.905
but try to understand that this is the truth.

23:27.675 --> 23:30.152
This has been going on for the past so many years.

23:30.177 --> 23:31.801
It has no meaning.

23:31.890 --> 23:33.888
If there has been any foolishness going on for the past so many years

23:33.913 --> 23:35.814
are you still going to do this foolishness?

23:35.917 --> 23:37.276
Has it helped you in any way?

23:38.244 --> 23:39.258
Another thing is

23:39.283 --> 23:40.764
as I was telling Dr. Sahab

23:40.789 --> 23:42.817
Everybody says, It has never been so earlier.

23:42.842 --> 23:44.675
If it has not been so, but it will be so someday.

23:44.944 --> 23:47.835
It will take place some day.

23:47.860 --> 23:49.455
Whenever it will take place

23:49.480 --> 23:51.093
it will be said that it didn't happen earlier.

23:51.118 --> 23:52.517
Should it take place just after its birth?

23:52.620 --> 23:54.688
Should it take place just after the world creation?

23:55.720 --> 23:58.080
Such type of arguments go on like this.

23:58.105 --> 24:01.299
Because of that If a person wants to run away from Sahaj yoga

24:01.323 --> 24:04.335
the door is open for him but he who wants to sit

24:04.360 --> 24:05.509
there is a a seat reserved for him.

24:05.535 --> 24:07.857
All of you settle down.

24:07.882 --> 24:09.971
I want all of you to settle down perfectly in Sahajyoga.

24:10.052 --> 24:12.911
This is the first thing. Everything happens later on.

24:15.232 --> 24:16.232
and settle down people.

24:17.686 --> 24:19.742
As you said: Maa you came in the form of flame.

24:19.767 --> 24:21.161
What will flame do single handed?

24:21.186 --> 24:22.717
Many flames are required.

24:22.742 --> 24:24.990
We need many flames from one flame.

24:25.015 --> 24:27.264
Only then there will be light.

24:27.542 --> 24:29.226
Had it been possible by ME alone

24:29.251 --> 24:33.302
Why would I have requested you people to settle down?

24:33.556 --> 24:38.037
One who prays to God for the betterment, move ahead smoothly

24:38.062 --> 24:40.295
You only are on the stage, not I

24:40.320 --> 24:43.729
You are on the stage. The world is watching you.

24:44.021 --> 24:46.880
Understand that the world is watching you, not to ME.

24:47.408 --> 24:51.012
They have taken that out, saying that this is Devi.

24:51.037 --> 24:53.400
I cannot be Devi.

24:53.425 --> 24:56.162
The point is that they have made a Devi

24:56.187 --> 24:58.475
Rest you handle.

25:03.586 --> 25:07.272
Delhiites are otherwise also sitting on the stage on their own.

25:07.281 --> 25:09.445
on the throne

25:09.470 --> 25:12.343
Bakasurs are sitting on the stage.

25:12.442 --> 25:13.790
They are sitting in the gallery.

25:13.815 --> 25:17.811
You are sitting on the threshold of God

25:17.836 --> 25:20.396
You sit there. People will watch you only.

25:20.421 --> 25:24.932
People sitting on the threshold

25:24.957 --> 25:28.047
will watch what are people living in Delhi doing?.

25:28.072 --> 25:33.057
It is a great responsibility.

25:33.082 --> 25:35.380
There is a great responsibility on people living in Delhi.

25:35.405 --> 25:37.709
What do you have to say?

25:37.968 --> 25:43.747
Lekhak ji (writer) Yes, say!

25:43.772 --> 25:47.853
Yes, write down

25:47.878 --> 25:49.473
(UNCLEAR)

25:49.519 --> 25:52.229
It is the best

25:52.301 --> 25:55.146
Deepa didn't come today?

25:55.171 --> 25:56.841
She is in Dharmshala

25:56.929 --> 25:58.509
Shri Mataji: She is in Dharamshala.

25:58.534 --> 26:01.192
S.Y: She is much better.

26:08.365 --> 26:09.365
