31:04.377 --> 31:15.857
Shankh Chakra Gadda Haste, Maha Laxmi Namostute

31:15.905 --> 31:22.593
Maha Laxmi Namostute

31:22.618 --> 31:26.343
Shri Mataji: Beautiful! You people have started singing in Sanskrit

31:26.368 --> 31:27.609
It is great!

31:27.937 --> 31:41.021
Don't become Pandits now. It is really great!

31:41.101 --> 31:47.192
Actually, voice is vibrating.

31:47.495 --> 31:54.077
Because of the vibrations, it is cooling.

31:54.601 --> 31:58.561
When you sing you feel vibrates, your voice reverberates.

31:58.586 --> 32:00.296
The same is the case with him too.

32:00.321 --> 32:02.452
When he had sung earlier it was not so

32:02.477 --> 32:10.341
but since he is in (Sahaj) his voice vibrates.

32:10.714 --> 32:13.466
It is like a echo

32:14.514 --> 32:20.620
It is called PRATISATH in Sanskrit.

32:20.645 --> 32:26.251
Beautiful! He is doing so great!

32:26.276 --> 32:31.705
Such pronunciation of Sanskrit

32:31.776 --> 32:33.864
I have not heard such pure pronunciation among Punjabis.

32:33.889 --> 32:37.999
I am telling you the truth.

32:38.024 --> 32:40.704
I too have studied in Punjab.

32:40.911 --> 32:43.875
The language of that place is such

32:44.494 --> 32:47.776
And even Hindi speaking people pronounce SPASHT as ASPASHAT

32:48.110 --> 32:52.272
But I have never heard such pure pronunciation in Sanskrit language.

32:52.297 --> 32:54.194
I am telling you the truth. It is great!

32:54.218 --> 32:57.640
It is great! It should be so.

33:03.751 --> 33:10.021
S.Y: Basically, Mother it is the effort of Rajesh.

33:10.148 --> 33:13.988
He has started after coming here only.

33:14.013 --> 33:16.334
(UNCLEAR)

33:16.731 --> 33:19.893
Shri Mataji: Look at Rajesh as well!

33:19.918 --> 33:23.164
Now a days he is studying Gyaneshwari.

33:24.680 --> 33:28.597
S.Y: He is the one who started (UNCLEAR) Last time when he came,

33:28.653 --> 33:31.863
Rustam and he came that was the day this whole started.

33:31.895 --> 33:32.518
Shri Mataji: Oh! Really!

33:32.543 --> 33:33.380
S.Y: About a week ago.

33:33.405 --> 33:38.631
Then started Sanskrit. Rustam didn't know DEVNAGRI LIPI(script)

33:38.671 --> 33:39.540
Can you imagine?

33:39.565 --> 33:42.078
He didn't know Devnagri.

33:42.103 --> 33:45.194
He never studied Devnagri. He studied in English school

33:45.258 --> 33:46.303
then stayed in England.

33:46.328 --> 33:47.869
He didn't know Devnagri.

33:47.894 --> 33:48.779
He studied Sanskrit

33:48.804 --> 33:51.068
and is writing MY names in Sanskrit.

33:51.094 --> 33:53.535
He has already written one thousand names.

33:54.386 --> 33:55.961
S.Y: Has Rustam written?

33:55.986 --> 34:00.371
Shri Mataji: Yes, He has written one thousand names.

34:00.530 --> 34:01.767
S.Y: He is a Sanskrit scholar.

34:01.792 --> 34:03.089
Shri Mataji: He has become a Sanskrit scholar

34:03.137 --> 34:04.137
S.Y: And very inspired.

34:04.225 --> 34:06.613
Shri Mataji: Yes, even Gregoire!

34:06.878 --> 34:11.051
Gregoire has become a Sanskrit scholar.

34:11.815 --> 34:13.672
Absolutely Sanskrit scholar.

34:16.612 --> 34:22.624
How does the result of Sahajyoga come out?

34:22.776 --> 34:24.312
Because one who doesn't know even Devnagri

34:24.344 --> 34:26.479
Gregoire never not even Hindi words

34:26.526 --> 34:28.899
It is worth noticing, how beautifully he writes!

34:30.778 --> 34:33.523
One who didn't know even A,AA,I,EE (Devnagri Script)

34:34.438 --> 34:35.438
How did it happen?

34:35.477 --> 34:38.496
Our Babba doesn't know Urdu at all.

34:38.521 --> 34:39.474
I still know a little bit of it.

34:39.499 --> 34:40.725
not even a little bit of Urdu.

34:40.750 --> 34:44.357
But the poetry he has done in Urdu

34:44.388 --> 34:44.964
You listen to him.

34:44.989 --> 34:47.727
MY brother, he is a Chartered accountant.

34:47.783 --> 34:50.295
He didn't know even the name of poetry, what is poetry

34:50.485 --> 34:53.754
He was just like a stone hearted in this field.

34:53.779 --> 34:56.643
He writes (Poetry) so beautifully, so marvelous.

34:57.902 --> 34:59.695
(UNCLEAR)

34:59.963 --> 35:01.407
He has started writing very deep (poetry)

35:01.828 --> 35:04.167
He has named himself 'Dilosh'

35:04.192 --> 35:05.945
means NIRMAL

35:08.926 --> 35:11.099
named himself, very good (poetry) he writes.

35:11.124 --> 35:15.090
MY brother himself wonders, where do YOU get these words from?

35:15.188 --> 35:15.956
says: i don't know.

35:15.981 --> 35:16.643
says I give him.

35:16.668 --> 35:18.567
I said some words I too don't know.

35:18.592 --> 35:24.675
How does one know? It is so great!

35:24.800 --> 35:26.520
He has started writing very nicely.

35:26.545 --> 35:28.659
It is so surprising how. How does one bloom?

35:28.770 --> 35:31.638
(UNCLEAR) poetry I never expected from him.

35:31.663 --> 35:35.479
He is a Chartered accountant.

35:35.556 --> 35:39.665
Except Math and counting he has heard no other sound.

35:39.690 --> 35:41.483
I don't know from where he got this thing.

35:41.980 --> 35:43.726
And says, i go on writing.

35:43.751 --> 35:45.556
Now he is writing in Marathi.

35:45.581 --> 35:49.336
His Marathi language was so weak, that I used to write his essays.

35:49.387 --> 35:52.552
He is writing in Marathi.

35:52.577 --> 35:55.719
He is writing in Hindi, but out of all, the best he writes in Urdu.

35:56.847 --> 35:58.479
[ SHERO SHAYIRI ] poet's expression in poetic manner

35:58.504 --> 36:00.696
and there are no rhyming words at all.

36:03.022 --> 36:05.780
It should be said that there is actual poetry in him.

36:05.805 --> 36:07.318
Actual poetry!

36:07.517 --> 36:09.841
There is nothing useless

36:09.866 --> 36:10.946
Nothing useless!

36:10.971 --> 36:13.542
Do you see this MILAN KI SHAYIRI (poetry of union) we have got?

36:13.567 --> 36:16.499
The earlier poetry was all about gloominess

36:16.524 --> 36:17.925
VIRAH KI SHAYIRI [poetry of separation]

36:17.950 --> 36:19.349
Now it is poetry of union.

36:19.878 --> 36:22.615
You set it in his song

36:23.424 --> 36:26.011
There are so many

36:26.442 --> 36:29.956
but they were not so popular.

36:35.172 --> 36:37.606
S.Y: It is coming right from the heart.

36:37.631 --> 36:39.108
He is writing right from the heart.

36:40.003 --> 36:40.500
Shri Mataji saying about HER brother:

36:40.627 --> 36:43.498
It is remarkable for him to write poetry.

36:43.523 --> 36:46.640
I know he is conditioning poetry very well.

36:46.663 --> 36:49.961
Because of Marathi he had little difficulty

36:49.986 --> 36:52.218
I used to sit with him to teach him poetry.

36:52.243 --> 36:55.819
I would tell him that by telling you, I will lose my poetry.

36:55.844 --> 36:57.562
It doesn't enter even your head.

36:57.618 --> 37:00.476
He would ask: Why do they write?

37:00.501 --> 37:02.251
Why don't they write in a straight forward manner?

37:02.276 --> 37:05.279
writing about moon and this and that in a twisted manner

37:05.305 --> 37:06.316
it is better to say

37:06.340 --> 37:09.648
it seems (UNCLEAR)

37:09.673 --> 37:10.851
When he was young

37:10.876 --> 37:12.400
when he was in Matric

37:12.479 --> 37:14.919
(UNCLEAR)

37:14.944 --> 37:17.195
Would say why did they need to write all this?

37:17.220 --> 37:18.824
It has caused my headache.

37:18.849 --> 37:21.210
If one has to learn this Marathi language

37:21.235 --> 37:21.959
it is a great headache.

37:21.984 --> 37:22.803
I would tell him don't learn Marathi

37:22.828 --> 37:24.371
He would say it is compulsory, what to do?

37:24.396 --> 37:27.088
Such was his condition.

37:27.502 --> 37:30.461
In Marathi he would just pass or fail.

37:31.371 --> 37:32.850
He is good at Mathematics.

37:32.875 --> 37:34.764
But I could not understand

37:34.789 --> 37:37.232
from where this new flower has bloomed.

37:37.286 --> 37:41.408
It happened like this that somewhere

37:41.433 --> 37:46.024
you can say for example that a lotus has bloomed out of a rose

37:46.049 --> 37:51.442
(UNCLEAR)

37:51.467 --> 37:56.908
It is like that, can't understand anything

37:56.933 --> 38:00.065
But it means, what an unusual, strange and

38:00.090 --> 38:02.244
an unprecedented event is going on.

38:02.268 --> 38:04.605
but like this something must come out of everybody.

38:04.630 --> 38:07.166
some miracles should take place, then it will be recognized.

38:07.912 --> 38:10.284
He (singer) is also saying that he will tell some miracle

38:10.309 --> 38:11.945
A great miracle he has come across.

38:11.970 --> 38:14.412
S.Y: Yes, really!

38:14.437 --> 38:16.048
Shri Mataji: What you are saying

38:16.073 --> 38:18.644
the reason for that is only that you are NISHKALANK (pure)

38:18.824 --> 38:20.841
Nobody can disgrace you!

38:20.866 --> 38:24.396
If somebody tries, he cannot disgrace you.

38:24.476 --> 38:29.586
Nobody can disgrace you, even a little bit

38:29.611 --> 38:32.420
Even if you think that this person is disgracing you

38:32.445 --> 38:35.723
You will see that this disgrace will be on his face.

38:38.553 --> 38:41.851
In Illustrated Weekly Rajneesh sent a woman

38:41.876 --> 38:44.181
bribed her, to interview ME.

38:44.205 --> 38:46.765
and made a third Muslim lady to write

38:46.790 --> 38:48.712
and in that some wrong statements were

38:48.737 --> 38:51.327
that SHE is such

38:51.352 --> 38:55.667
HER ways are such that SHE mesmerizes. All nonsense.

38:55.691 --> 38:57.249
My husband got very angry.

38:57.274 --> 38:59.590
Especially, my brother took a dagger.

38:59.616 --> 39:02.234
Both of them said, "Now we have to drag them to the court."

39:02.259 --> 39:04.073
I told them, I am not going to the court.

39:04.098 --> 39:06.109
If you want to put up a case, you go, I am not going to the court.

39:06.181 --> 39:07.185
(UNCLEAR)

39:07.210 --> 39:08.623
I asked them what will you do?

39:08.649 --> 39:10.929
There in London people told them

39:10.954 --> 39:13.354
that they should put up a case for ten lakhs.

39:13.629 --> 39:14.863
I said, " I won't go to the court."

39:14.895 --> 39:16.641
You do whatever you want to do.

39:16.666 --> 39:17.895
It is not going to pay you any dividend.

39:17.920 --> 39:19.038
I made them to understand a lot.

39:19.063 --> 39:21.760
I told Rajesh to talk to them.

39:21.785 --> 39:23.803
Tell them to ask for forgiveness

39:23.828 --> 39:25.502
so that this matter will be over.

39:25.527 --> 39:27.654
I don't like this court business.

39:28.230 --> 39:30.086
When nobody came to any agreement

39:30.111 --> 39:33.202
The Illustrated Weekly came to closure for six months.

39:33.266 --> 39:35.520
And they had a loss in terms of Crores.

39:40.734 --> 39:45.494
Then their employees went on a strike.

39:46.186 --> 39:49.345
Then they sent a message.

39:49.370 --> 39:52.500
They are saying why you had written against our Mataji

39:52.525 --> 39:53.769
we will go on strike.

39:53.794 --> 39:55.516
I said that they have written long back.

39:55.541 --> 39:57.459
Why are you going on a strike now?

39:57.568 --> 40:00.028
Already they have been punished

40:00.053 --> 40:02.561
But they won't change.

40:03.183 --> 40:06.339
You have to set right first of all, newspaper agencies.

40:06.694 --> 40:09.384
Now you tell ME what is the need to write what Rajneesh is saying?

40:09.805 --> 40:14.058
Now a days it is Ravan UVACHA (what did Ravana say?)

40:14.083 --> 40:17.326
S.Y: That is a fact.

40:17.351 --> 40:20.199
Shri Mataji: This is the Geeta of modern times.

40:20.569 --> 40:22.347
What useless he is talking?

40:22.372 --> 40:23.871
They get a lot of pleasure by publishing it.

40:23.896 --> 40:25.164
Don't know why?

40:25.599 --> 40:27.444
And now a days he is in Goa.

40:27.469 --> 40:29.429
Now a days we can see some more people.

40:29.454 --> 40:31.020
As bed bugs multiply

40:31.045 --> 40:34.697
so can be seen two to four such people in Poona.

40:34.906 --> 40:36.170
They will all be taken into account.

40:36.195 --> 40:39.051
They will surely reach Poona.

40:39.076 --> 40:41.389
Poona!

40:41.414 --> 40:44.675
They are coming out at wrong place.

40:46.302 --> 40:47.240
All this

40:47.265 --> 40:48.772
Their techniques are like

40:48.797 --> 40:51.480
it appears to be like a group

40:51.949 --> 40:53.596
They help each other.

40:53.621 --> 40:55.544
We too should have our strong group.

40:55.569 --> 40:57.645
Question doesn't arise that anybody can touch you!

40:57.670 --> 40:58.972
We should live like this.

40:59.280 --> 41:00.571
We are all one.

41:00.596 --> 41:01.563
We should have one aim.

41:01.588 --> 41:03.347
We should know this aim.

41:03.372 --> 41:06.823
Then you will enjoy your dividends yourself.

41:07.584 --> 41:11.437
But when we don't know that aim, we face problems.

41:14.158 --> 41:15.249
We have come to Delhi.

41:15.274 --> 41:17.046
We have to do something or the other here.

41:17.071 --> 41:18.461
It is New Year!

41:18.486 --> 41:21.115
You do whatever you desire.

41:21.141 --> 41:22.941
In the evening we have pujan

41:22.966 --> 41:24.957
We will see then.

41:24.982 --> 41:29.158
But all these desires should be for the betterment of everyone.

41:30.185 --> 41:32.926
Not for yourself, I take care of you.

41:32.951 --> 41:35.788
There is no worry about you. It should for everyone.

41:35.916 --> 41:37.372
It should be for the group.

41:37.397 --> 41:38.762
It should be for others.

41:38.787 --> 41:39.898
Not for yourself.

41:39.923 --> 41:41.692
You for yourself have (surrendered to ME)

41:41.717 --> 41:44.808
You said that you have surrendered yourself to ME

41:44.872 --> 41:48.084
I am already managing you.

41:51.410 --> 41:53.720
You have to take care of the whole world.

41:53.745 --> 41:57.517
Specially, We have to take care of Delhi.

41:58.840 --> 42:01.279
Is it okay!
